Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.name: benefitText
Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.abstract: Set the description that user is going to get benefit with product registration. If multilple benefits are there, please provide the content separated by \n. To be displayed at screen PR-1a.(Please refer to the flow document for more info).

Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.name: extendWarrantyText
Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.abstract: Set the description along with extended warranty after successful registration of product. To be displayed at screen PR-4b.(Please refer to the flow document for more info). The default localized text for the key PRG_Extended_Warranty_Lbltxt will be displayed in case vertical is not providing the description.

Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.name: emailText
Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.abstract: Set the description about what information user will get via email. To be displayed at screen PR-4b.(Please refer to the flow document for more info). The default localized text for the key PRG_Eamil_Sent_Lbltxt will be displayed in case vertical is not providing the description.

Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.name: mandatoryRegisterButtonText
Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/c:.abstract: Set the button text of the product registeration button in case if mandatoryProductRegistration is set to true. To be displayed at screen PR-4b.(Please refer to the flow document for more info).

Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/s:.name: mandatoryProductRegistration
Classes/PPRContentConfiguration.html#/s:.abstract: Set the value as true and false to hide the No Thanks, Register Later button.(Please refer to the flow document for more info).
